CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 10, 1965, pg. 24, reads: "PETE MARACINI INC., Budweiser Distributor for the Pittsburgh area, welcomes a new member to their Pittsburgh area selling team. Henry Gitnik (right), president, and Jack Smith (left) welcome Jay Barbour (center) to their sales team. The new member will undergo intensive training in product knowledge, merchandising and salesmanship. PETE MARACINI INC., has been the Budweiser Distributor in the Pittsburgh market since 1964.
TitMainTitle: Jack Smith, and Jay Barbour shaking hands with Henry Gitnik in Pete Maracini Inc., Budweiser distributor office
